# Optional: only needed to turn on the "Connect Google Drive" button in
# My Account (master and client). Without these, the app works fully —
# the Drive card just shows a "not configured yet" note and the "Skip
# for now" link lets clients past the setup screen.
#
# Get these from https://console.cloud.google.com:
#   1. Create a project → enable "Google Drive API" and "Google Picker API".
#   2. Create an OAuth 2.0 Client ID (type: Web application) and add your
#      deployed domain (e.g. https://teamify-hrms.vercel.app) under
#      "Authorized JavaScript origins".
#   3. Create an API key and restrict it to the Drive/Picker APIs.
VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=
VITE_GOOGLE_API_KEY=
